	HOLTSINGER RH, ELLISON GW. spontaneous pneumothorax. Compendium of Continuing Education: Practica Veterinaria 1995;17:197-210;
	MANNING MM, BRUNSON DB. barotrauma in a cat. Journal of American Veterinary Medicins Association 1994; 205:62-64;
	HANCE SR, ROBERTSON JT. subcutaneous emphysema from an axillary wound that resulted in pneumomediastinum and bilateral pneumothorax in a horse. Journal of American Veterinary Medicins Association 1992;200:1107-1110.
	KRAMEK BA, CAYWOOD DD. pneumothorax. Veterinary Clinicians of North America: Small Animal Practice 1987;17:285-300;
	GUARD C. pneumothorax after parturition in a cow. Compendium of Continuing Education: Practica Veterinaria 1985;7:s191-s194.

